Anna Rosemond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Rosemond 0 Anna Rosemond (February 16, 1886 – 1966) was one of the earliest film actresses of the early silent film era. Anna Miers Rosemond was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Her father was an Austrian immigrant, her mother a first generation American of German parentage.
